						<td width="80%">
							<div class="col-md-3">
								{{view "select" required=true class="form-control" prompt="请选择"
								content=model.isCreateVmData value=model.vmFormData.IsShowVmFunction optionValuePath="content.id"
								optionLabelPath="content.name" }}
							</div>
							<div class="col-md-6" style="margin-top: 5px;">
								<span>如选择“否”，CloudBoot平台将不再显示任何虚拟机相关的信息</span>
							</div>
						</td>
					</tr>

